      "content": "but it's not just a mistake you \"learn\" from. it's my whole identity. the people i worked with, the prestige, the discoveries... it's all gone. it's like i've been living a ghost story. i look in the mirror and there's nothing there. just an empty shell of a man who wasted a decade chasing a shadow. it feels like the only honest thing left to do is just... admit it's finished.",
